00:32:18,990 --> 00:32:22,650
Because the time we've been together is still too short, and you still haven't graduated yet.

375
00:32:22,650 --> 00:32:26,970
You might not be very clear on this, your mom has some opinions towards me. I haven't thought through how to resolve this yet.

376
00:32:26,970 --> 00:32:29,260
If I go and mention marriage to her right now,

377
00:32:29,260 --> 00:32:32,510
