378
00:32:32,510 --> 00:32:36,390
My mom is prejudiced towards you? How do you know that?

379
00:32:37,460 --> 00:32:39,660
I guessed it.

380
00:32:39,660 --> 00:32:42,230
I thought you don't know.

381
00:32:43,390 --> 00:32:47,550
The matter of marriage, let's put it off for now. I can fulfill your other terms.

382
00:32:47,550 --> 00:32:49,780
I think you kind of misunderstood.

383
00:32:49,780 --> 00:32:53,540
