387
00:33:00,870 --> 00:33:05,260
Every morning he goes to walk the dog. We can't let him find us! If he finds out, I'm dead!

388
00:33:07,610 --> 00:33:10,630
Easy there, don't hit anything.

389
00:33:12,690 --> 00:33:16,770
