390
00:33:16,770 --> 00:33:20,420
When you don't hear anything, then sneak back in.

391
00:33:23,500 --> 00:33:26,380
Then first, move away your head.

392
00:33:31,260 --> 00:33:34,700
Let's go, Summer! Slow down, slow down!

393
00:33:34,700 --> 00:33:36,410
Go.

394
00:33:39,550 --> 00:33:42,770
That's right. It's me. That's right, yes.

395
00:33:42,770 --> 00:33:45,980
- Don't reveal any leverage.
- Xiao Han?

396
00:33:45,980 --> 00:33:48,740
Uncle Tong? Wait a moment.

397
00:33:48,740 --> 00:33:51,040
Okay. Let's end it here for today!

398
00:33:52,270 --> 00:33:56,290
- Uncle Tong!
- Why are you here so early in the morning?

399
00:33:57,240 --> 00:34:00,500
I was... just passing by here.

400
00:34:00,500 --> 00:34:02,270
And came to look around.

401
00:34:02,270 --> 00:34:06,330
Just passing by and came to look around?

402
00:34:06,330 --> 00:34:08,770
You tell me the truth.

403
00:34:08,770 --> 00:34:12,000
Is it that in your heart you still cannot forget Nian Nian?

404
00:34:12,000 --> 00:34:13,980
Uncle, don't misunderstand.

405
00:34:13,980 --> 00:34:17,950
I... really was just driving by. I thought...

406
00:34:19,310 --> 00:34:24,050
I suddenly thought of when I sent Nian Nian home before, and it brought back memories.

407
00:34:25,110 --> 00:34:27,090
Uncle, you need to believe me.

408
00:34:27,090 --> 00:34:30,130
My feelings towards Nian Nian are really more serious than what you guys think.

409
00:34:30,130 --> 00:34:33,850
Actually, you two haven't known each other for that long.

410
00:34:33,850 --> 00:34:37,760
Once time passes, you will definitely be able to forget her.

411
00:34:37,760 --> 00:34:42,470
