412
00:34:42,470 --> 00:34:44,220
<i>Dad... hurry and leave!</i>

413
00:34:44,220 --> 00:34:46,550
<i>Uncle here is speaking from the heart. I know, Uncle.</i>

414
00:34:46,550 --> 00:34:51,420
