422
00:35:12,130 --> 00:35:14,830
It can't be helped, from the standpoint of being a parent.

423
00:35:14,830 --> 00:35:16,500
You tell me!

424
00:35:16,500 --> 00:35:18,370
You tell me how I'm suppose to feel.

425
00:35:18,370 --> 00:35:21,750
