426
00:35:21,750 --> 00:35:24,830
I am her dad! Right?

427
00:35:24,830 --> 00:35:26,660
Be more understanding, child.

428
00:35:26,660 --> 00:35:29,420
It's nothing, it's nothing. It will pass. Okay?

429
00:35:29,420 --> 00:35:31,260
It will pass.

430
00:35:37,850 --> 00:35:40,840
