434
00:35:50,760 --> 00:35:55,110
I'm telling you, I hope that my words have reached you.

435
00:35:55,110 --> 00:35:59,830
- My heart feels much better. Thank you Uncle, for enlightening me.
- That's good, that's good.

436
00:35:59,830 --> 00:36:03,800
- Look, my phone is ringing again! Really...
- Pick it up!

437
00:36:03,800 --> 00:36:07,530
- Okay. Then I will leave first, Uncle. I will leave first!
- Okay!

438
00:36:07,530 --> 00:36:09,700
Okay, I'll come over now. Okay.

439
00:36:09,700 --> 00:36:11,940
If your heart feels unwell, call me at anytime, okay?

440
00:36:11,940 --> 00:36:13,840
Okay, okay!

441
00:36:13,840 --> 00:36:16,300
Bye Uncle!

442
00:36:25,800 --> 00:36:28,180
Nian Nian.

443
00:36:28,180 --> 00:36:30,290
